name: TULE's Tutorial Of Cyberspace
description:
Thank you for scanning my code in the ACTIVATOR MAGAZINE! Doing so I assume you are on a mobile device. If you wish to download this game you must open this page on a WINDOWS computer. If you are not here from the Activator magazine, thank you for checking out my work!

This is TULE's tutorial. where you will learn how to navigate the demi-planes of CYBERSPACE! 

Thank you for picking up the art issue and trying out my work.
